sub_title: BA European Studies with a minor on Gender and Diversity Studies in Maastricht University.
summary:
A curious social scientist with a passion for gender philosophy, diversity and culture. 

I am a passionate individual, who is prompt by new challenges and opportunities that develop my skill-set and perspective. A challenging deadline highly motivates me to dive in so the job is done, with enough time to polish the project.

I am dedicated and hard working, in any position or situation I have worked. From small workshops and seminars, to music festivals and charity events, I work well with others as a team member or on my own initiative.
